{
  "text": "Can you tell me what the result of the application of the Law of Squares is to those figures? The number is approximately meaningless in the finite sense as there are many, many digits. It, however, constitutes a great calling which we of all creation feel and hear as if our own entities were distorted towards a great and overwhelming sorrow. It demands our service.",
